          "emoji": "ğŸ’¡",
          "id": 21,
          "text": "This app was developed with great attention to detail. Not only regarding the visible part (UI) of the app, but also when it comes to the code behind the scenes.\n\nWe put special attention to properly saving and restoring the application state after a configuration change.\n\nWe therefore encourage you, to try rotating the screen or switching to dark mode (*) while running our app.\n\nYou will notice, that the state is perfectly restored in any situation. (Yes, we actually made sure that it always works.)\n\n* About the dark mode: This app provides support for system wide dark (or night) mode. Try it out by turing on dark mode in your settings.",
