        {
          "emoji": "ğŸ’¾",
          "id": 20,
          "text": "A special feature integrated into our note app is the option to import and export all data.\n\nWe would like you, to try this feature by following these three simple steps:\n\n1. Export all data (for example to Google Drive) by clicking on the menu at the top.\n(You have to leave this note editor first.)\n\n2. Change or delete some of the content in the app.\n\n3. Re-import the data from the the file that was generated in the first step.\n\nYou will notice, that we actually made the file access and share content functionality of Android work. And it\u0027s reliable, just like the rest of this app.",
